<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Dispute outcome — PCN <%= pcn_number %></title>
</head>

<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f8f8f8; font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;">
  <div style="background-color:#f8f8f8; padding:40px 20px;">
    <div style="max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; background-color:#ffffff; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div style="background:#1C1917; padding:32px 24px; text-align:center;">
        <!-- LOGO PLACEHOLDER -->
      </div>

      <!-- Result Badge -->
      <div style="padding:28px 24px 0; text-align:center;">
        <div style="display:inline-block; background-color:#fef2f2; border:1px solid #fca5a5; border-radius:20px; padding:8px 20px;">
          <span style="color:#7f1d1d; font-size:14px; font-weight:600;">Dispute Rejected</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div style="padding:28px 32px;">
        <h2 style="font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#111827; margin-bottom:12px;">
          Hi <%= user_name %>,
        </h2>

        <p style="font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:#374151; margin-bottom:8px;">
          We want to be straightforward with you. The council or operator has reviewed your dispute for PCN <strong><%= pcn_number %></strong> and has not upheld it.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size:16px; line-height:1.7; color:#374151; margin-bottom:24px;">
          This is not the result we were aiming for, and we understand this is frustrating. Here is where things stand and what your options are.
        </p>

        <!-- PCN Result Card -->
        <div style="background-color:#fff7f7; border:2px solid #fca5a5; border-radius:10px; padding:20px; margin-bottom:28px;">
          <p style="margin:0 0 6px; font-size:13px; color:#991b1b; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.05em;">Case Summary</p>
          <p style="margin:0 0 20px; font-size:20px; color:#7f1d1d; font-weight:700;"><%= pcn_number %></p>

          <div style="border-top:1px solid #fecaca; padding-top:16px;">
            <table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse;">
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:7px 0; font-size:14px; color:#991b1b;">Operator</td>
                  <td style="padding:7px 0; font-size:14px; color:#111827; font-weight:600; text-align:right;"><%= operator_name %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:7px 0; font-size:14px; color:#991b1b;">Grounds Submitted</td>
                  <td style="padding:7px 0; font-size:14px; color:#111827; font-weight:600; text-align:right;"><%= dispute_reason %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:7px 0; font-size:14px; color:#991b1b;">Outcome</td>
                  <td style="padding:7px 0; font-size:14px; color:#b91c1c; font-weight:600; text-align:right;">Not upheld</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:7px 0; font-size:15px; color:#7f1d1d; font-weight:700;">Amount Due</td>
                  <td style="padding:7px 0; font-size:15px; color:#7f1d1d; font-weight:700; text-align:right;"><%= full_penalty_amount %></td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- What happens next -->
        <h3 style="font-size:16px; font-weight:600; color:#111827; margin-bottom:14px;">Your options from here</h3>

        <table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; margin-bottom:24px;">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:0 16px 16px 0; vertical-align:top; width:20px;">
                <div style="width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:#FF6900; margin-top:7px;"></div>
              </td>
              <td style="padding-bottom:16px; vertical-align:top;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 4px; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#111827;">Escalate to the Traffic Penalty Tribunal</p>
                <p style="margin:0; font-size:14px; color:#6b7280; line-height:1.6;">If you feel the decision was procedurally incorrect, you have the right to appeal to an independent adjudicator. The TPT is free to use and its decisions are binding on the council. Contact us and we can assess whether escalation is warranted.</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:0 16px 0 0; vertical-align:top; width:20px;">
                <div style="width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:#9ca3af; margin-top:7px;"></div>
              </td>
              <td style="vertical-align:top;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 4px; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:#111827;">Pay the fine</p>
                <p style="margin:0; font-size:14px; color:#6b7280; line-height:1.6;">If you prefer to close the matter, you can pay through Settlfines or directly via the operator portal. Please be aware of any payment deadlines noted in the rejection correspondence to avoid further charges.</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <p style="font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; color:#6b7280; margin-bottom:28px;">
          If you have received a formal rejection notice, keep it safe — you will need the reference number if you choose to escalate.
        </p>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div style="text-align:center; margin-top:32px;">
          <a href="<%= cta_url %>"
            style="display:inline-block; background-color:#1C1917; color:#ffffff; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; padding:14px 32px; border-radius:10px; text-decoration:none;">
            Review Your Case
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div style="background-color:#f9fafb; padding:24px 32px; border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <p style="margin:0 0 8px; font-size:13px; color:#6b7280; text-align:center;">
          Settlfines — automated parking fine dispute platform
        </p>
        <p style="margin:0; font-size:12px; color:#9ca3af; text-align:center;">
          &copy; 2026 Settlfines Ltd. This is a system-generated notification.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
